<p class="p">For the purposes of generality and meaningful ranking of the composite indicators we assume 
 <div id="IEq14" class="inline-formula" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <alternatives class="alternatives" xmlns="">
   <tex-math id="M31" class="tex-math">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal} \usepackage{amsmath} \usepackage{wasysym} \usepackage{amsfonts} \usepackage{amssymb} \usepackage{amsbsy} \usepackage{mathrsfs} \usepackage{upgreek} \setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt} \begin{document}$$y_{d}$$\end{document}</tex-math>
   <div id="M32" class="math" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    <div class="msub">
     <span class="mi">y</span>
     <span class="mi">d</span>
    </div>
   </div>
   <span xlink:href="40064_2015_1536_Article_IEq14.gif" class="inline-graphic" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
  </alternatives>
 </div> follows a Beta distribution in the range (0, 1) as 
 <div id="IEq15" class="inline-formula" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <alternatives class="alternatives" xmlns="">
   <tex-math id="M33" class="tex-math">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal} \usepackage{amsmath} \usepackage{wasysym} \usepackage{amsfonts} \usepackage{amssymb} \usepackage{amsbsy} \usepackage{mathrsfs} \usepackage{upgreek} \setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt} \begin{document}$$y_{d}$$\end{document}</tex-math>
   <div id="M34" class="math" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    <div class="msub">
     <span class="mi">y</span>
     <span class="mi">d</span>
    </div>
   </div>
   <span xlink:href="40064_2015_1536_Article_IEq15.gif" class="inline-graphic" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
  </alternatives>
 </div> is positive valued and potentially skewed (Iyengar 1982). The probability density of the Beta distribution is as follows:
 <disp-formula id="Equ3" class="disp-formula">
  <label class="label">3</label>
  <alternatives class="alternatives">
   <tex-math id="M35" class="tex-math">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal} \usepackage{amsmath} \usepackage{wasysym} \usepackage{amsfonts} \usepackage{amssymb} \usepackage{amsbsy} \usepackage{mathrsfs} \usepackage{upgreek} \setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt} \begin{document}$$f(z) = \frac{{z^{a - 1} (1 - z)^{b - 1} {\text{d}}x}}{B(a,b)},\quad 0 &lt; z &lt; 1\;{\text{and}}\; a,b &gt; 0$$\end{document}</tex-math>
   <div id="M36" display="block" class="math" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    <div class="mrow">
     <span class="mi">f</span>
     <div class="mrow">
      <span stretchy="false" class="mo">(</span>
      <span class="mi">z</span>
      <span stretchy="false" class="mo">)</span>
     </div>
     <span class="mo">=</span>
     <div class="mfrac">
      <div class="mrow">
       <div class="msup">
        <span class="mi">z</span>
        <div class="mrow">
         <span class="mi">a</span>
         <span class="mo">-</span>
         <span class="mn">1</span>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="msup">
        <div class="mrow">
         <span stretchy="false" class="mo">(</span>
         <span class="mn">1</span>
         <span class="mo">-</span>
         <span class="mi">z</span>
         <span stretchy="false" class="mo">)</span>
        </div>
        <div class="mrow">
         <span class="mi">b</span>
         <span class="mo">-</span>
         <span class="mn">1</span>
        </div>
       </div>
       <span class="mtext">d</span>
       <span class="mi">x</span>
      </div>
      <div class="mrow">
       <span class="mi">B</span>
       <span stretchy="false" class="mo">(</span>
       <span class="mi">a</span>
       <span class="mo">,</span>
       <span class="mi">b</span>
       <span stretchy="false" class="mo">)</span>
      </div>
     </div>
     <span class="mo">,</span>
     <span width="1em" class="mspace"/>
     <span class="mn">0</span>
     <span class="mo">&lt;</span>
     <span class="mi">z</span>
     <span class="mo">&lt;</span>
     <span class="mn">1</span>
     <span width="0.277778em" class="mspace"/>
     <span class="mtext">and</span>
     <span width="0.277778em" class="mspace"/>
     <span class="mi">a</span>
     <span class="mo">,</span>
     <span class="mi">b</span>
     <span class="mo">&gt;</span>
     <span class="mn">0</span>
    </div>
   </div>
   <graphic xlink:href="40064_2015_1536_Article_Equ3.gif" position="anchor" class="graphic" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
  </alternatives>
 </disp-formula>where 
 <div id="IEq16" class="inline-formula" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
  <alternatives class="alternatives" xmlns="">
   <tex-math id="M37" class="tex-math">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal} \usepackage{amsmath} \usepackage{wasysym} \usepackage{amsfonts} \usepackage{amssymb} \usepackage{amsbsy} \usepackage{mathrsfs} \usepackage{upgreek} \setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt} \begin{document}$$B(a,b) = \mathop \smallint \nolimits_{0}^{1} x^{a - 1} (1 - x)^{b - 1} {\text{d}}x.$$\end{document}</tex-math>
   <div id="M38" class="math" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    <div class="mrow">
     <span class="mi">B</span>
     <div class="mrow">
      <span stretchy="false" class="mo">(</span>
      <span class="mi">a</span>
      <span class="mo">,</span>
      <span class="mi">b</span>
      <span stretchy="false" class="mo">)</span>
     </div>
     <span class="mo">=</span>
     <div class="msubsup">
      <span largeop="false" class="mo">âˆ«</span>
      <div class="mrow">
       <span class="mn">0</span>
      </div>
      <span class="mn">1</span>
     </div>
     <div class="msup">
      <span class="mi">x</span>
      <div class="mrow">
       <span class="mi">a</span>
       <span class="mo">-</span>
       <span class="mn">1</span>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="msup">
      <div class="mrow">
       <span stretchy="false" class="mo">(</span>
       <span class="mn">1</span>
       <span class="mo">-</span>
       <span class="mi">x</span>
       <span stretchy="false" class="mo">)</span>
      </div>
      <div class="mrow">
       <span class="mi">b</span>
       <span class="mo">-</span>
       <span class="mn">1</span>
      </div>
     </div>
     <span class="mtext">d</span>
     <span class="mi">x</span>
     <span class="mo">.</span>
    </div>
   </div>
   <span xlink:href="40064_2015_1536_Article_IEq16.gif" class="inline-graphic" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
  </alternatives>
 </div>
</p>
